    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Connect
    Backend class allowing for database connection and closure.
    Employee
    Backend class for accessing and manipulating employee table values as well as creating and inserting new orders to both the order_info and order_items tables
    EmployeeView
    EmployeeView class represents the panel used by employees to take and manage orders.
    GUI
    Frontend class for initializing the base GUI that exists for all views.
    Inventory
    Backend class for accessing and manipulating raw_inventory table values
    ManagerView
    Frontend class for creating the manager view in the GUI.
    MenuItem
    Backend class which handles many functions pertaining to the menu_item and item_price tables in the database
    Order
    Backend class for generating X-Reports and Z-Reports
